## 5️⃣ Database 모듈

### ❌ 이전
```typescript
db.createTable(name, schema);
db.insert(table, data);
db.select(table).where(...);
```

### ✅ 새로운 API
```typescript
import { Database } from 'freelang-v4';

Database.createTable(name, schema);
Database.insert(table, data);
Database.query(table, (row) => row.field === value);
```

---

## 6️⃣ Crypto 모듈

### ❌ 이전
```typescript
crypto.createHash('sha256');
crypto.createHmac('sha256', key);
```

### ✅ 새로운 API
```typescript
import { Crypto } from 'freelang-v4';

Crypto.hash(data, 'sha256');
Crypto.hmac(data, key, 'sha256');
Crypto.encrypt(data, key);
Crypto.uuid();
```

